/>\n你考幾點</blockquote><br />\n12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽聞食飯前多數考元朗邨，正野喎</blockquote><br />\n其實我仲未記得晒路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥多</blockquote><br />\n你學左幾多堂</blockquote><br />\n10堂   齋路試咋 <br />\n最驚d盲毛亂過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我學左11堂<br />\n感覺好唔實在"},{"pid":"5f2178f897ea483daeae90b1a2f745503d7aed4b","tid":251631,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"1堂幾耐？<br />\n靠咩車？"},{"pid":"32af0d0c6ec62453a2cf9c2fbe6bbc23a254e59c","tid":251631,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"考咩車?"},{"pid":"a0aeaffa95cc8cae61a6be758343f31df650a0ac","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考咩車?</blockquote><br />\n一堂兩節<br />\n45分鐘一節<br />\n棍van呀"},{"pid":"54b0f91dcccec97ee1639f4f3e1326456a9f12b0","tid":251631,"uid":17862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"上youtube 睇多次考試路線"},{"pid":"0a124175a7da3e96a8ecd43c957c733863ce76aa","tid":251631,"uid":17862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"一出學院轉二波，第一個路口轉左前要上過三波"},{"pid":"d6bed7ef52861edb8e2713005332097367ee233c","tid":251631,"uid":17862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"咪有個位要連cut 兩條線既，記住cut 完一條，望清楚先再cut 另一條"},{"pid":"bd721480560d8cb9a1bd51585ab8fb61a7244161","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上youtube 睇多次考試路線</blockquote><br />\n路線就記熟了<br />\n但好怕臨考做左on9<br />\n可能入錯波<br />\n可能拉左手制但忘記空波<br />\n又怕唔停一停唔記得落反一波起步<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737efd7637347e38aa017db8ada16a4347586eb7","tid":251631,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"信我<br />\n考牌官講完咩都回佢係 大聲d但又有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc15d425d5855d8be639d6f3a3df018b87778e2","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信我<br />\n考牌官講完咩都回佢係 大聲d但又有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知道巴打"},{"pid":"441667f7f2e04f50f93fe4cf10834376ec8a7884","tid":251631,"uid":66083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"宏業東條路慢慢黎啦, 過死車個陣對頭有車咪停係死車後面等到冇晒車先過囉<br />\n轉彎都係慢慢黎望清楚有冇死車停係出灣位, 因為好多時D 24噸,拖頭遮住你視線, 心急出入彎突然有車出黎比考官踩停咁就玩完啦<br />\n<br />\n工業村整路如果有臨時燈位, 都要做過死車動作, 打燈另頭盲點, 大大條直路上3波就一定但小心超速(唔好過50, 行得順踩到45左右就好收喇)<br />\n<br />\n考官講乜你都禮貌上回一回佢OK或收到啦~"},{"pid":"8e22c9e29c234595a063d7c6d4eb0976d8b64f3d","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪有個位要連cut 兩條線既，記住cut 完一條，望清楚先再cut 另一條</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知道巴打"},{"pid":"6682a67a8c01ae7cc9cb0a9469f8ad8297101219","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宏業東條路慢慢黎啦, 過死車個陣對頭有車咪停係死車後面等到冇晒車先過囉<br />\n轉彎都係慢慢黎望清楚有冇死車停係出灣位, 因為好多時D 24噸,拖頭遮住你視線, 心急出入彎突然有車出黎比考官踩停咁就玩完啦<br />\n<br />\n工業村整路如果有臨時燈位, 都要做過死車動作, 打燈另頭盲點, 大大條直路上3波就一定但小心超速(唔好過50, 行得順踩到45左右就好收喇)<br />\n<br />\n考官講乜你都禮貌上回一回佢OK或收到啦~</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知道巴打<br />\n<br />\n始終好怕衰on9野<br />\n<br />\n今日一出學院，側邊有架車其中一個轆掂到我條行車線，我冇做過死車步驟，因為我覺得好大條路，夠位過，但師父話考試有機會已經肥左"},{"pid":"5e686d242a2a032feb56e8b3549795a06a7d8472","tid":251631,"uid":67653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"緊張真係冇得救，我都緊張到手震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得得閒冇野做就望吓鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac26211a37004251435b1bc3bfc532d99c96776","tid":251631,"uid":100943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T17:52:41.000Z","msg":"巴打我考3點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算唔算好時間？ 都係元朗駕院 thanks"},{"pid":"21abee33f27aa1a8cfe94fe0f40f2eac8280c392","tid":251631,"uid":17862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"巴打 加油，等你好消息"},{"pid":"0ff5a47d88a189d7806446173f6b2a8a4ad802cc","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我考3點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算唔算好時間？ 都係元朗駕院 thanks</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c824911f83afac5698e9447267d1893005741add","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 加油，等你好消息</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e8d6d026d89de8af841b150ba2df6620926dc4","tid":251631,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n我都考元朗，不過排到年尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未學"},{"pid":"362e73d73c6501fd1cacc6b5b2b6574b69ba1b80","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油<br />\n我都考元朗，不過排到年尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未學</blockquote><br />\n我師父話補考要排半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67312ba0c4fa7bb1e71466545561eafe6da49f17","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加油<br />\n我都考元朗，不過排到年尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未學</blockquote><br />\n我師父話補考要排半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n至少半年"},{"pid":"e1c4529e2775a84edeb9e314937da013b13e7e8b","tid":251631,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好考前上一堂熱身<br />\n緊張就深呼吸</blockquote><br />\n考9點9<br />\n考之前得反45分鐘一節，淨係係學院練掉頭泊位斜路</blockquote><br />\n邊間？我果間考之前得試車 早一日就係最尾果堂<br />\n不過1take pass<br />\n考路試記得有禮貌,唔好懶醒"},{"pid":"47683bae8317a6b1db7f0b19b908fcc782764ae2","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最好考前上一堂熱身<br />\n緊張就深呼吸</blockquote><br />\n考9點9<br />\n考之前得反45分鐘一節，淨係係學院練掉頭泊位斜路</blockquote><br />\n邊間？我果間考之前得試車 早一日就係最尾果堂<br />\n不過1take pass<br />\n考路試記得有禮貌,唔好懶醒</blockquote><br />\n元朗駕院呀<br />\n師父話9點半前運輸處規定冇得出街練車"},{"pid":"9a0e54a2868cb5a2d6d87af414bec5a23d021f31","tid":251631,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過死車記住一米距離<br />\n如果前面左右都有車 你覺得無一米距離 一定唔好行 肥硬</blockquote><br />\n宏業東兩邊都會有死車<br />\n唔行點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左右都要有一米距離，並且超龜速地不停望左右"},{"pid":"1cf5b5bed173487f3423edd753a17f85ec8860a6","tid":251631,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最好考前上一堂熱身<br />\n緊張就深呼吸</blockquote><br />\n考9點9<br />\n考之前得反45分鐘一節，淨係係學院練掉頭泊位斜路</blockquote><br />\n邊間？我果間考之前得試車 早一日就係最尾果堂<br />\n不過1take pass<br />\n考路試記得有禮貌,唔好懶醒</blockquote><br />\n元朗駕院呀<br />\n師父話9點半前運輸處規定冇得出街練車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n0600-0730 可以學"},{"pid":"06403f469253b8e7f55e043b0a827514e06d186f","tid":251631,"uid":66083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打我考3點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算唔算好時間？ 都係元朗駕院 thanks</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第2 take考係3點2, 小心係入汽站排隊的的士同小巴"},{"pid":"ffa76a0bcbbb3ed4a264beef6136210c7a432c11","tid":251631,"uid":50872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我考3點半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算唔算好時間？ 都係元朗駕院 thanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多車到仆街 good luck"},{"pid":"8c82432b901c5fe78a09665016af4a75c0979255","tid":251631,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"1. 慢慢揸，一個鐘先返到考場都唔撚驚，最緊要慢。<br />\n2.  小路出大路記得有車要讓，話之佢有幾百架車黎緊，老遠見到都等佢過埋先。<br />\n3. 你個柒頭每5米要大幅度左右望<br />\n4. 唔撚洗驚後車比既壓力，揸住個主權，由你創造條車龍出黎。<br />\n<br />\n加油安答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d74c9bd5719b6bd20c0b97387cf0c568445bac6","tid":251631,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"講低幾點邊條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我地扮下過馬路，如果有突發野又處理到仲唔即刻有分加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c9fe28aa72a7df538dd1d51ccb8bec78f83c82","tid":251631,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 慢慢揸，一個鐘先返到考場都唔撚驚，最緊要慢。<br />\n2.  小路出大路記得有車要讓，話之佢有幾百架車黎緊，老遠見到都等佢過埋先。<br />\n3. 你個柒頭每5米要大幅度左右望<br />\n4. 唔撚洗驚後車比既壓力，揸住個主權，由你創造條車龍出黎。<br />\n<br />\n加油安答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔慢得，上次考個考官叫我揸返快啲，太慢唔得"},{"pid":"6b40d60a707bdb03738179dfdf430de776b7fe83","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"