","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 慢慢揸，一個鐘先返到考場都唔撚驚，最緊要慢。<br />\n2.  小路出大路記得有車要讓，話之佢有幾百架車黎緊，老遠見到都等佢過埋先。<br />\n3. 你個柒頭每5米要大幅度左右望<br />\n4. 唔撚洗驚後車比既壓力，揸住個主權，由你創造條車龍出黎。<br />\n<br />\n加油安答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔慢得，上次考個考官叫我揸返快啲，太慢唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪老點人啦<br />\n<br />\n一定要跟返交通情況控制車速<br />\n<br />\n泊車你就可以慢"},{"pid":"22e5618bcef3b2b69d1531883f4b8df2b6246dde","tid":251631,"uid":4477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edd51b81ee51ab27204ff292ecff0188c9f27e4f","tid":251631,"uid":36583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 慢慢揸，一個鐘先返到考場都唔撚驚，最緊要慢。<br />\n2.  小路出大路記得有車要讓，話之佢有幾百架車黎緊，老遠見到都等佢過埋先。<br />\n3. 你個柒頭每5米要大幅度左右望<br />\n4. 唔撚洗驚後車比既壓力，揸住個主權，由你創造條車龍出黎。<br />\n<br />\n加油安答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每5米左右望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該即肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e739233294325e4a9f73bc7e39ed6573ea85386c","tid":251631,"uid":30022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"停車後落返一波唔該"},{"pid":"0b64ef3c6effa3e8effab95e44337409a0d3e2cf","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>停車後落返一波唔該</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日忘記"},{"pid":"5ec15349e4d190ef3790aea8434d9bb38eb93a61","tid":251631,"uid":70689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>停車後落返一波唔該</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日忘記</blockquote><br />\n呢d忘記冇辦法<br />\n始終係習慣黎<br />\n不過個考官應該唔會落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你就要諗諗有咩未做<br />\n<br />\n臨考前都係上youtube睇晒元朗路線<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LNI0FNGa_Os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLNI0FNGa_Os&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordKy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=62a3b70a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LNI0FNGa_Os</a>"},{"pid":"d605d636375931cca5f4771c6e7906bb83be584c","tid":251631,"uid":50872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"12月頭考車<br />\n幾月開始學好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6aafb092cf8658291970b1ccb160e7d334c639e","tid":251631,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"上禮拜學車見聞 想提提師兄你<br />\n工業邨個整路位<br />\n就算你行緊左線都小心右邊有架癲狗的士閘埋黎cut鳩你線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dba7f31085b4e5246a04992d01d553efc3858cc","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T23:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上禮拜學車見聞 想提提師兄你<br />\n工業邨個整路位<br />\n就算你行緊左線都小心右邊有架癲狗的士閘埋黎cut鳩你線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知道巴打<br />\n訓得好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e040f8284d29d6e658b282e83a1bac94b5d8b752","tid":251631,"uid":42732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T23:46:29.000Z","msg":"我係元朗考廢牌1 take pass左，主要係睇死車多唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我考果日好少，少到唔尋常，唔知係咪有其他考生報左警抄牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dc6ee67acd766dd5e688f27953b1a8405a897b","tid":251631,"uid":67653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要超車，停車前面留返兩三米 <br />\n唔係會肥接近物體同急速扭軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /