-05-23T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問，考忠義街有咩要注意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主你要一take pass吖</blockquote><br />\n我pass左呀<br />\n你都努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f39b44b1288f01d7829884b63d3fe88c45fa90","tid":251631,"uid":68786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"今日考沙駕1 tick pass 好開心 成個人鬆哂<br />\n<br />\n一開頭好緊張，泊位泊撚到歪撚哂但又未踩界 <br />\n調頭ok，出到去路口考官話轉左做斜路開停，我唔知做乜鳩轉撚左右出學院，佢即時話轉左喎，唉算啦直出去啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行河畔，惠康路口轉右有成班自由行想過又唔過，但又突左少少出來，我打燈望鏡盲區踩左線再同樣動作右轉番，之後大致順利都係避下死車。<br />\n之後大直路仲死左一次火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過極速著番車。<br />\n<br />\n等緊個陣以為會肥點知pass左<br />\n結論係仆街唔緊要，冷靜識執生最重要。"},{"pid":"fee9b48884cca7076b3c63df63af4c27e1008cf8","tid":251631,"uid":66083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>考邊條呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n元朗邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好彩</blockquote><br />\n我之前都係pass呢條 最易呢條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第2 TAKE都係PASS呢條, 咁都抽中呢條行你真係好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabefc069d73ab984ec0fc798ea9e60f0ae483b8","tid":251631,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日考沙駕1 tick pass 好開心 成個人鬆哂<br />\n<br />\n一開頭好緊張，泊位泊撚到歪撚哂但又未踩界 <br />\n調頭ok，出到去路口考官話轉左做斜路開停，我唔知做乜鳩轉撚左右出學院，佢即時話轉左喎，唉算啦直出去啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行河畔，惠康路口轉右有成班自由行想過又唔過，但又突左少少出來，我打燈望鏡盲區踩左線再同樣動作右轉番，之後大致順利都係避下死車。<br />\n之後大直路仲死左一次火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過極速著番車。<br />\n<br />\n等緊個陣以為會肥點知pass左<br />\n結論係仆街唔緊要，冷靜識執生最重要。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好睇考官<br />\n我聽個FD 講佢試過CUT線 無望盲區<br />\n比人屌 諗住肥更最尾都比佢PASS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cafe2267a33f788b97ead43de39fc331ef39ad","tid":251631,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>考邊條呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n元朗邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好彩</blockquote><br />\n我之前都係pass呢條 最易呢條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第2 TAKE都係PASS呢條, 咁都抽中呢條行你真係好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師父話好似乜部做得好有好印象，丙部會行條好路線"}]}